data.description: Two for one buy down offer! Seller is offering $5,200 closing cost credit and buy down rate! A true ranch with three bedrooms on the main floor and two additional non-conforming rooms in the basement. Great starter home, 10 min away from highway and legends shopping center, and located at the end of the street (cul de sac) with no neighbors behind and to the side of the home. Huge fenced backyard for gardening, family gathering or your pets to run around. Newly installed furnace, air conditioning unit (June 2023) and water heater (2019). Roof was replaced in 2017. Home is being sold in present condition. Bring the family to come see this move-in ready home!
